    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is an absolute dream\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and kept in truly pristine shape, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to tell you more about it!",
