    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the marque, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L high-revving inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a perfectly synchronized VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock, ensuring precise power delivery to the rear wheels. The chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement to mitigate structural fatigue, while the suspension geometry is maintained by refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. Every mechanical component, from the cooling system's expansion tank to the high-pressure fuel lines, adheres to factory tolerances. This vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the purist, offering a visceral driving experience and showroom-level mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 43900.0,
