    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously garaged and shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior features a flawless factory finish with a deep, mirror-like luster, recently enhanced by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin retains its original 'new car' scent; the premium leather upholstery is supple and entirely free of creases, wear, or fading. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. With zero curb rash on the wheels and brand-new performance tires, this car offers a driving experience indistinguishable from a new vehicle. Complete with all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a comprehensive service history.",
      "price": 48500.0,
